OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773436322
OL,3,CPlea from RSPCA as cattery in Kent
OL,4,Cfaces closure
OL,6,FThe RSPCA says a cattery in Kent is
OL,7,Ffacing closure with a fundraising
OL,8,Fappeal underway.
OL,10,FThe Ashford Garden Cattery was opened
OL,11,Fin May 2006 and has helped to re-home
OL,12,Faround 6,000 cats over the years.
OL,14,FThe animal centre, based in Station
OL,15,FRoad, Ashford, is run by the RSPCA's
OL,16,FAshford and District Branch.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
