OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773436322
OL,3,CPlea from RSPCA as cattery in Kent
OL,4,Cfaces closure
OL,6,FThe charity says the centre lost
OL,7,Faround #30,000 last year because of
OL,8,Frises in the cost of living including
OL,9,Fincreasing veterinary bills and also
OL,10,Fthe general downturn in donations.
OL,12,FTrustees say that unless the centre
OL,13,Fcan raise an initial #50,000 it could
OL,14,Fbe forced to close its doors at the
OL,15,Fend of the year.
OL,17,FSecretary of the Branch Trustees,
OL,18,FSally Moir, says a consultation has
OL,19,Fstarted with the centre's six staff in
OL,20,Fa bid to reduce costs.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773436322
OL,3,CPlea from RSPCA as cattery in Kent
OL,4,Cfaces closure
OL,6,FVolunteers are also being told about
OL,7,Fthe issues facing the cattery.
OL,9,FShe said: "Last year we lost #30,000
OL,10,Fand our predicted loss this year could
OL,11,Fbe #50,000 and while the branch has
OL,12,Freserves they will only last so long.
OL,14,F"As well as our cattery which has re-
OL,15,Fhomed thousands of cats in its time,
OL,16,Fwe run a pet food bank and offer
OL,17,Fwelfare and neutering services to pet
OL,18,Fowners who are struggling financially.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773436322
OL,3,CPlea from RSPCA as cattery in Kent
OL,4,Cfaces closure
OL,6,F"Our focus is on providing a high-
OL,7,Fquality rehoming service for cats,
OL,8,Fmany of whom are brought to us by
OL,9,FRSPCA inspectors after being rescued
OL,10,Ffrom cruelty and neglect.
OL,12,F"The demand for our services just
OL,13,Fkeeps on going up and up with the big
OL,14,Frise in cruelty cases our inspectors
OL,15,Fwitnessed last year contributing to
OL,16,Fthat.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773436322
OL,3,CPlea from RSPCA as cattery in Kent
OL,4,Cfaces closure
OL,6,F"We have been full to capacity with
OL,7,Fcats for long periods of time,
OL,8,Falthough every day we get emails and
OL,9,Fphone calls from people wanting to
OL,10,Fgive up their cats, while we also deal
OL,11,Fwith abandoned cats, pregnant mothers
OL,12,Fand kittens that need hand-rearing.
OL,14,F"We try to help try to help as many as
OL,15,Fwe can but we are always full up."
OL,17,FShe added: "While our veterinary costs
OL,18,Fhave soared, our fundraising has
OL,19,Fdropped, which has meant our losses
OL,20,Fkeep on growing.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773436322
OL,3,CPlea from RSPCA as cattery in Kent
OL,4,Cfaces closure
OL,6,F"Unless we get an injection of funds
OL,7,Fwe will not have much choice but to
OL,8,Fclose the cattery at the end of this
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,F"That will be a huge blow to the Kent
OL,12,Fcommunity and cat lovers from a wider
OL,13,Farea too who have relied on our
OL,14,Fservices.
OL,16,F"Regrettably, in a bid to cut our
OL,17,Fcosts we are talking to our staff to
OL,18,Fidentify savings.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1773436322
OL,3,CPlea from RSPCA as cattery in Kent
OL,4,Cfaces closure
OL,6,F"But we are really hopeful that people
OL,7,Fwill rally round and help us by making
OL,8,Fa donation to our appeal."
